988 A.2d 511 Antonio Levar BROWN, Appellant v. STATE of Maryland, Appellee. No. 97

Sept.Term, 2009.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. Feb. 3, 2010.

ORDER

Having considered the parties’ joint motion for remand, it is this 3rd day of February, 2010, hereby ORDERED that:

(1) This matter is remanded to the Circuit Court for Carroll County pursuant to Rule 8-604(d); and

(2) That further proceedings be held consistent with the Joint Motion, above.
